Description: Up for grabs is a lightly used 2019 Gibson Les Paul Classic Goldtop with Zebra pickups! This guitar has all the Gibson flair you love and has a nice dark and classy rosewood board. The original owner is a collector and did not use this one too much! Check it! Serialized 190021872 9lbs 14oz  Includes original hardshell case and case goodies. The new 2019 Gibson Les Paul Classic boasts a traditional tone wood construction of a mahogany back and maple top coupled with a mahogany neck and bound rosewood fingerboard. A slim taper neck profile and 61 R and 61 T zebra pickups provide the playability and classic Gibson tones from the era, 4 push-pull control assembly give a sonic variety to this complete guitar package.
